    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的恶魔，在这款动作roguelike生存游戏中与无尽的敌人作战。探索不断变化的关卡，解锁新的强化和技能，每升一级都能让你变得更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在恶魔之书中解锁更多可玩角色！每个恶魔提供独特的游戏风格，具有一项被动技能和四项主动技能。无论你喜欢进攻、防守、被动或主动的玩法，掌握你恶魔的优势是推进关卡的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都是随机生成的，每次都会带来新的挑战。你会发现宝箱、陷阱、由敌人守卫的强大奖励和神秘装置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次升级可以从三个选项中选择一个强化。强化有两种形式：增益，提供被动提升，和变异，即自动触发的武器。将恶魔的技能与不同的强化组合，尝试新的构建方式，制造混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特色功能：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人PvE Roguelike： 体验紧张的玩家对环境战斗，拥有roguelike风格的进程。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与成群的敌人作战： 在充满混乱和动作的战斗中面对无情的敌人浪潮。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的可玩恶魔： 解锁并扮演强大的恶魔，每个恶魔都拥有独特的技能组合和游戏风格。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动武器和主动技能： 使用自动武器（变异）并掌握各种主动技能来消灭敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多样化区域： 在充满宝藏、挑战和惊喜的不断变化的环境中探索。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁内容： 随着游戏进程解锁更多可玩角色、强化和其他内容。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限构建可能性： 将恶魔技能与强化组合，尝试不同的构建和策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素风弹幕射击混乱： 沉浸在复古灵感的像素艺术视觉效果中，体验紧张刺激的弹幕射击。</p></li></ul>",
